 6.
 Go to https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/windows/installer/5.7.html
 Select MySQL community edition, click to download on your local machine
 Follow the on-screen prompts to configure MySQL and enter your password.
 Finish the installation.
 Confirm by adding the software path into environment variables.
 Run the command to prompt the software specifications.
